songs.lyrics:
[Refrain]
Ayy, gang
Ayy, squad
(Sosa on the beat)
Gang, let's get it, let's get it
What you doing? Gang, Let's get it
Ayy, ayy
Ayy, ayy
Let's get it, let's get it, gang
Let's get it, let's get it

[Verse]
I'm DDB (Let's get it)
Bitch, you know about me (What?)
I hang in these streets
50 deep
No talk to police (At all)
[?] they shoot for me
OMG, I just killed this beat
Put it in disease (Let's get it)
In these streets (Let's get it)
You ain't in the streets
Boy, I'm in the streets, let's get it
Xans for the low, nigga (Xans for the low, low)
You can get these bitches, boy, two for four, nigga
You can get it from the window or the door (The window or the door)
Try some fu shit, lil bro gone blow
Talkin' like you got it boy you will get poked (You will get poked, bitch)
Seven dudes with me, who want smoke? (Man, who want smoke? Let's get it)
Green Glock, it's on go (This bitch on go)
Jimmy run up on 'em (Run up)
Shoot 'em in his nose (In his fuckin' nose, woo)
I'm ridin' with my TEC (Ridin' with this pretty TEC)
I ain't got no fuckin' type of respect (I ain't got respect, let's get it)
This bitch all up on me, I want neck
She just want the fame, that shit ain't shit (Let's get it)
Aye lil' bro let's do a hit (Let's do a hit, bitch)
He saying, "Fuck Dex" so we on that (Ayy, run up on him, let's get it)
He talkin' to the feds, he a snitch
Chop his fuckin' body, put it in a ditch, ayy (Let's get it)

[Refrain]
Ayy, gang
Ayy, squad
Gang, let's get it, let's get it
Squad, gang, squad
Ayy, gang
Ayy, ayy
Let's get it, let's get it, gang
Let's get it, let's get it

[Outro]
I'm DDB, Bitch you know about me
I hang in these streets
50 deep
No talk to police
Feds they shoot for me
OMG, I just killed this beat
songs.title: Faneto (Remix)
